    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 9th level, you learn to enable your team to become more aware of their surroundings and their enemies while working together. </p><p>While an ally is marked with your Exploit Weakness feature, they become aware of all creatures whom chakra you can sense as a result of the Sense Chakra special action. </p><p>Also, when you would activate a plan, you may treat your marked ally as if you were in their space when you activated it.</p>",
